metadata.name: Surreal HodgePodge
metadata.description:
This art depicts the "hodgepodge of surreal thoughts" in my mind.  
The water flowing represents the multiple flow of ideas.  
The text written in Greek on the old brown paper means 
"Let the waters have a dine with Lady whistle-wind"  
A fish swimming in my wine glass, represent "abundance" as it is associated with the water element.

Every item in this piece is a "hodgepodge of thoughts" that goes on, in my mind.
